{"type":"text","timestamp":1778990680336,"sessionID":"ses_1cbe4ba0fffey2cOczrfx74CqO","part":{"id":"prt_e341b79ac001TbU8We75iCR4bB","messageID":"msg_e341b6aef001NWfbRpxFsUOHsh","sessionID":"ses_1cbe4ba0fffey2cOczrfx74CqO","type":"text","text":"The issue is clear: rename one existing GO term to a species-agnostic label, add the requested narrow synonyms, and update the definition. Next I’m checking the current term, relevant patterns, and validation baseline before editing.","time":{"start":1778990676397,"end":1778990680333}}}
